    "The system message contains detailed instructions, feasible material combinations, and design knowledge that is critical for the DA to effectively use its knowledge base effectively.",
    "This knowledge, generated at different levels of quality using GPT-4, provides the DA with the context needed to optimize its design proposals (see section 3.1.2).",
    "The system message also explicitly states the objective of achieving maximum compressive strength and the requirements for the output format.The user (see Figure 3, center) provides laboratory validation feedback to the Assistant's recommendations.",
    "To streamline this process for systematic benchmarking, a table look-up has been employed in this work using established test results from the literature.",
    "These validation outcomes are provided to the Assistant as laboratory validation in the form of few-shot examples, i.e."
